&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/compatibility-error/"&gt;Compatibility Error&lt;/a&gt; — Gradle version mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/gradle/task-error/"&gt;Task Error&lt;/a&gt; — task execution failure&lt;/li&gt;
